@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 11A. Supervisor Review / Task Lifecycle

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> REQUEST_RECEIVED
REQUEST_RECEIVED --> IDEMPOTENCY_CHECKED : check_and_reserve_request
IDEMPOTENCY_CHECKED --> HITL_EVALUATING : new request
IDEMPOTENCY_CHECKED --> STREAMING : duplicate detected\n(returns existing task_id)

HITL_EVALUATING --> PLAN_FROZEN_FOR_REVIEW : review required
HITL_EVALUATING --> RUNNING : review not required
PLAN_FROZEN_FOR_REVIEW --> WAITING_REVIEW : snapshot stored

WAITING_REVIEW --> SNAPSHOT_VERIFIED : APPROVE
WAITING_REVIEW --> CANCELED : CANCEL
SNAPSHOT_VERIFIED --> RUNNING : resume_token + state_version valid
RUNNING --> COMPLETED
RUNNING --> FAILED

CANCELED --> [*]
COMPLETED --> [*]
FAILED --> [*]

note right of IDEMPOTENCY_CHECKED
Prevents duplicate task creation 
using Redis SET NX on request_id.
end note
@enduml

@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 11B. Supervisor Runtime Execution State Machine (Worker-internal)

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> DEQUEUED
DEQUEUED --> DIRECT_ANSWER_CHECKED
DIRECT_ANSWER_CHECKED --> COMPOSING : is_direct == True\n(Shortcut path)
DIRECT_ANSWER_CHECKED --> SELECT_NODE : is_direct == False

SELECT_NODE --> INVOKE_NODE : step exists
SELECT_NODE --> COMPOSING : no more steps

INVOKE_NODE --> HANDOFF_EVALUATE_NODE
HANDOFF_EVALUATE_NODE --> HANDOFF_APPLY_NODE : handoff detected
HANDOFF_EVALUATE_NODE --> MERGE_NODE : no handoff
HANDOFF_APPLY_NODE --> MERGE_NODE

MERGE_NODE --> SELECT_NODE : loop back

COMPOSING --> COMPLETED
COMPLETED --> [*]

note right of DIRECT_ANSWER_CHECKED
is_direct path:
- Skips downstream graph
- Directly calls LlmComposeService
- Efficient for simple greetings/answers
end note

note right of SELECT_NODE
LangGraph Node Mapping:
- select
- invoke
- handoff_evaluate
- handoff_apply
- merge
end note

note bottom
The runtime starts only after worker dequeues from TaskQueueService.
Approved snapshot resume skips planning and enters SELECT_NODE with frozen queue.
end note
@enduml
